nent legal guardians may apply when children are 14 days to 14 years old.*Lock in an affordable premium that will never increase. Build cash value and get double the coverageAs long as premiums are paid, your Grow-Up® Plan accumulates cash value.Coverage doubles during age 18 automatically - a $10,000 policy becomes $20,000 - with no increase in cost. Guaranteed coverage for lifeLifelong insurance protection as an adult, regardless of future health or occupation.Option to keep the policy as an adult and can purchase additional coverage, at our standard adult rates, regardless of future health or occupation. Get a Free Quote* If your child is between 15 and 17, please check out our Young Adult PlanLearn More About Life Insurance for Children     Child Life Insurance Benefits Do children need life insurance? Find out why you may want to consider children’s life insurance.Learn More    Gain Cash Value With Grow-Up® Plan Did you know that the Gerber Life Grow-Up® Plan builds cash value over time? Discover how this can help give your child a head start.Learn More    Questions About Life Insurance Considering life insurance? Make sure to get answers to these important questions
before you buy a policy.Learn More  View All Child Life Insurance Resources Gerber Life Grow-Up® Plan FAQs   What kind of insurance does the Grow-Up® Plan provide?The Grow-Up® Plan is a whole life insurance policy for a child that builds cash value. You are the policy owner until your child reaches age 21. At that time, he or she becomes the policy owner.Is my child required to buy additional life insurance?No. Your child’s whole life insurance continues as long as premiums are paid. As an adult, your child is guaranteed the option to buy additional life insurance protection at our standard age-based rates.Can Gerber Life cancel my child’s Grow-Up® Plan coverage?Once coverage begins, and as long as the premiums are paid, Gerber Life cannot cancel the Grow-Up® Plan for any reason. Only you (or your child at age 21) can cancel coverage.View All Gerber Life Grow-Up® Plan Questions Get a Free QuoteHighly recommended by customers   View All Gerber Life Grow-Up® Plan Reviews View All Gerber Life Grow-Up® Plan Reviews Get a Free QuoteStart Now! 1. Apply Today Our simple application only takes minutes to complete.2. Tell Us About Your Child Answer a few questions about your child.3. Enter Your Contact Information Provide a few details about yourself and your application is done! Get a Free Quote




