Murry S. Gerber



Mr. Murry S. Gerber is Independent Director at United States Steel Corp., Independent Director at Halliburton Co., and Independent Director at BlackRock, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at United States Steel Corp., Halliburton Co., BlackRock, Inc., Augustana College (Illinois), and The Pittsburgh Cultural Trust.
Mr. Gerber was previously employed as Chief Executive Officer by Coral Energy LLC, Chairman by Pennsylvania Business Council, and Treasurer by Shell Oil Co. He also served on the board at EQT Corp. and Allegheny Conference on Community Development.
He received his undergraduate degree from Augustana College (Illinois) and a graduate degree from the University of Illinois.



