Murray Auto Body Repair
Gerber Collision & Glass Murray - 4460 South 500 West repair center offers quality collision auto body repair services backed by a National Lifetime Guarantee for as long as you own your vehicle. We repair all makes and models and provide free written repair estimates. Contact our Murray auto body shop for all of your auto collision repair requirements.

Collision Repair Murray
Gerber Collision & Glass Murray services include collision repair, auto body repair, dent / scratch repair / removal, frame straightening, auto paint repair, paintless dent repair (PDR), bumper repair, and more, to bring your vehicle back to pre-accident condition. We are your full service collision auto body shop, located in Murray.
Why Choose Gerber in Murray?

FREE Repair Estimates
National Lifetime Guarantee
Direct Billing to Insurance
Interest Free Financing (up to 6 mths)
Rental Car Assistance
I-CAR Certified


Collision Repair Shop Murray
When you require auto collision repair expertise in Murray, UT, choose Gerber Collision & Glass. Our Murray collision repair center is I-CAR Gold Class Certified, which is the highest training level recognized in the collision repair industry. For expert auto body service that comes with a National Lifetime Guarantee, insist on Gerber Collision & Glass in Murray, UT.
